{"iti40:0.1":"Itivuttaka 40 ","iti40:0.2":"Dukanipata ","iti40:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","iti40:0.4":"Vijjasutta ","iti40:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti40:2.1":"“Avijja, bhikkhave, pubbangama akusalanam dhammanam samapattiya anvadeva ahirikam anottappam; ","iti40:2.2":"vijja ca kho, bhikkhave, pubbangama kusalanam dhammanam samapattiya anvadeva hirottappan”ti. ","iti40:2.3":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti40:2.4":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti40:3.1":"“Ya kacima duggatiyo, ","iti40:3.2":"asmim loke paramhi ca; ","iti40:3.3":"Avijjamulika sabba, ","iti40:3.4":"icchalobhasamussaya. ","iti40:4.1":"Yato ca hoti papiccho, ","iti40:4.2":"ahiriko anadaro; ","iti40:4.3":"Tato papam pasavati, ","iti40:4.4":"apayam tena gacchati. ","iti40:5.1":"Tasma chandanca lobhanca, ","iti40:5.2":"avijjanca virajayam; ","iti40:5.3":"Vijjam uppadayam bhikkhu, ","iti40:5.4":"sabba duggatiyo jahe”ti. ","iti40:6.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti40:6.2":"Tatiyam. ","iti40:6.3":"Pathamabhanavaro. "}